OL,3,CJury in Natalie McNally murder trial
OL,4,Cretires to consider verdict
OL,6,FThe jury in the trial of the man
OL,7,Faccused of the murder of Natalie
OL,8,FMcNally has retired to consider its
OL,9,Fverdict.
OL,11,FMs McNally, 32, was 15 weeks pregnant
OL,12,Fwhen she was beaten and stabbed at her
OL,13,Fhome in Lurgan on December 18 2022.
OL,15,FStephen McCullagh, 36, of Woodland
OL,16,FGardens in Lisburn, has denied
OL,17,Fmurdering Ms McNally, who had been
OL,18,Fpregnant with his child.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
