OL,3,CJury in Natalie McNally murder trial
OL,4,Cretires to consider verdict
OL,6,FDuring the four-week trial, the
OL,7,Fprosecution claimed that McCullagh
OL,8,Fmurdered Ms McNally after setting up a
OL,9,F"false alibi" that he was
OL,10,Flivestreaming a video gaming session
OL,11,Fon YouTube.
OL,13,FThe defence has instead asserted that
OL,14,Fa former boyfriend of Ms McNally, who
OL,15,Fcannot be named, was responsible for
OL,16,Fher murder.
OL,18,FJudge Mr Justice Patrick Kinney
OL,19,Ffinished delivering his charge to the
OL,20,Fjury on Monday morning.
