OL,3,CJury in Natalie McNally murder trial
OL,4,Cretires to consider verdict
OL,6,FHe said jurors must consider all the
OL,7,Fevidence presented to them to decide
OL,8,Fwhether they are satisfied beyond
OL,9,Freasonable doubt that the defendant
OL,10,Fwas responsible for Ms McNally's
OL,11,Fmurder.
